{"tid":648034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"巧遇清水健 《五體不滿足》乙武洋匡當場被驗身證實暗藏巨根","createTime":"2018-04-30T10:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T11:11:41.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"12bcd5bbd563b23ff36469452e63de2753f617db","tid":648034,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"現年42歲的身障作家乙武洋匡，雖身體殘疾但不向命運低頭，不但考上早稻田大學，更獲得美滿家庭，他將經歷寫成《五體不滿足》出版成冊，激勵眾多失意之人，沒想到前年爆出外遇新聞，還遭指偷吃超過50名女性，讓他形象崩壞，離婚收場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-04-30/656/20180430001815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-04-30%2F656%2F20180430001815.jpg&h=2db534b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然乙武洋匡並未因此隱居，他上周末精神奕奕現身日本影音網站Niconico舉辦的「超會議」，不但參加會談，還四處趴趴走逛攤位，甚至過程中還暢飲啤酒，被網友譏說他「酒駕」，而在現場，乙武洋匡遇上了AV一線男神清水健，兩人相遇果然迸出奇妙的火花。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/04/db46d66cd8e727e68312d4e942be2abd-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fdb46d66cd8e727e68312d4e942be2abd-600x400.jpg&h=e06efa32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清水健遇上乙武洋匡，想當然提出發揮「專業」，要求幫乙武洋匡驗身，隨即便在眾目睽睽之下，對大作家的身體摸來摸去，一度摸到重要部位，這是Mercedes-AMG近期推出的輕型油電動力系統，採用的是一具3.0L直列六缸渦輪增壓引擎，清水健竟露出驚訝表情，隨後將兩人當天的側拍照上傳推特，認證直呼：「乙武先生的GG好大啊！(他讓我摸啦)」，乙武洋匡則俏皮回應：「討厭啦」，網友看了則說出金句：「五體不滿足，那根大滿足」。"},{"pid":"6c12dd51508b2572380c8cb916c03e48035dc95a","tid":648034,"uid":35930,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"這是Mercedes-AMG近期推出的輕型油電動力系統，採用的是一具3.0L直列六缸渦輪增壓引擎，<br />\n<br />\n正呀"},{"pid":"7a6678cfb5e37eafa127bc7b697257a132680ffa","tid":648034,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c12dd51508b2572380c8cb916c03e48035dc95a","tid":648034,"uid":35930,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"這是Mercedes-AMG近期推出的輕型油電動力系統，採用的是一具3.0L直列六缸渦輪增壓引擎，<br />\n<br />\n正呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"原來係生化改造人"},{"pid":"03059719bd805b7b44b679087a8c03029db0220d","tid":648034,"uid":1049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"五體不滿足，下體大滿足.jpg"},{"pid":"cf99895e91336e6b67bcbed3b9bd0d947751c54a","tid":648034,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:57:01.000Z","msg":"下套AV有新嘢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8acff6752e968cd823a1a39198634b6157fa99","tid":648034,"uid":39706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"又會肯比第二個男人摸嗰度...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be8b88bb58cd3f74878f6751fd12a1213f6dd31","tid":648034,"uid":172246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9d8acff6752e968cd823a1a39198634b6157fa99","tid":648034,"uid":39706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"又會肯比第二個男人摸嗰度...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"無手無腳反抗唔到"},{"pid":"c4b564080fe27b274f79db6eef71969226929b67","tid":648034,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔怪得食到50個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bdf21dedaf6221386f78636dcdfba21682716f","tid":648034,"uid":81698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9be8b88bb58cd3f74878f6751fd12a1213f6dd31","tid":648034,"uid":172246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9d8acff6752e968cd823a1a39198634b6157fa99","tid":648034,"uid":39706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"又會肯比第二個男人摸嗰度...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"無手無腳反抗唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img